      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same device geometry or a sufficiently similar predicate; operating conditions span the COU envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry as the COU device. Operating conditions in validation span the full COU envelope (2–6 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM). Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU without extrapolation."
